data.description: This is a must see large modular home built in 2004. This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house with 9” ceilings throughout, sits on 2.71 acres. It has a large kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances. Unfinished room above 2 car garage. Washer/dryer, and mounted TV in living room conveys. Lake Marion is accessible thru the subdivision dock. Large 54” porch overlooking large pond. The property is completely fenced and has an electric gate.
